    <p><u>Version 1.3</u> - 2022/03/20</p>
    <li>Changes in Configuration page - Resolution, comment & type can be configured together</li>
    <li>Existing resolution will be overwritten with the latest comments (to avoid duplicates)</li>
    <li>Comment and ticket type will auto-populate based on the selected resolution in Home & Search pages</li>
    <li>Added page to view all the configured resolutions</li>
    <li>Introduced ticket details by category for the selected month</li>
    <li>Handled validation for Ticket number field which will restrict any characters/special characters to post the data</li>
    <li>Incident & Request count label is removed while viewing data for All months (since values are not displayed in previous versions)</li>
    <li>Empty ticket search is handled which was previously routed to search page</li>
    <li>Added access key bindings for ease of access</li>
    <br>
    <p><u>Version 1.2</u> - 2022/02/27</p>
    <li>Introduced log capturing feature to trace all the actions performed by the users</li>
    <li>Minor code changes (to handle datatype conversion for Ticket number field - <i>Regression-Handled in v1.3</i>) & UI changes</li>
    <br>
    <p><u>Version 1.1.1</u> - 2022/01/24</p>
    <li>Added Incident and SR count for the month</li>
    #2022/01/27
